text: Kamil Rajnert (born 29 November 1976) is a Polish equestrian. He competed in two events at the 2004 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Poland Category:Equestrians at the 2004 Summer Olympics Category:People from Trzebiatów
